  "prompt": "What are the best Hindi songs to sing?",
  "response": "There are many beautiful and popular Hindi songs that are great for singing, whether you're performing at a gathering or just enjoying a karaoke session. Here are some of the best Hindi songs across various genres and eras that are often appreciated for their melody and lyrics:\n\n### Classic Hits\n1. **\"Tujhe Kitna Chahne Lage\"** - Kabir Singh\n2. **\"Lag Ja Gale\"** - Lata Mangeshkar\n3. **\"Kabhi Kabhi Aditi\"** - Jaane Tu... Ya Jaane Na\n4. **\"Pehla Nasha\"** - Jo Jeeta Wohi Sikandar\n5. **\"Mere Sapno Ki Rani\"** - Aradhana\n\n### Romantic Songs\n6. **\"Tum Hi Ho\"** - Aashiqui 2\n7. **\"Raabta\"** - Agent Vinod\n8. **\"Tera Ban Jaunga\"** - Kabir Singh\n9. **\"Tum Se Hi\"** - Jab We Met\n10. **\"Khuda Jaane\"** - Bachna Ae Haseeno\n\n### Upbeat and Dance Numbers\n11. **\"Kala Chashma\"** - Baar Baar Dekho\n12. **\"Badtameez Dil\"** - Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani\n13. **\"Dil Chori\"** - Sonu Ke Titu Ki Sweety\n14. **\"Morni Banke\"** - Badhaai Ho\n15. **\"Saudagar Sauda Kar\"** - Saudagar\n\n### Soulful and Melodic\n16. **\"Channa Mereya\"** - Ae Dil Hai Mushkil\n17. **\"Agar Tum Saath Ho\"** - Tamasha\n18. **\"Tera Hone Laga Hoon\"** - Ajab Prem Ki Ghazab Kahani\n19. **\"Ae Mere Humsafar\"** - Baazigar\n20. **\"Tujh Mein Rab Dikhta Hai\"** - Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi\n\n### Contemporary Favorites\n21. **\"Shayad\"** - Love Aaj Kal (2020)\n22. **\"Gulabi Aankhen\"** - R.D. Burman Classics\n23. **\"Khairiyat\"** - Chhichhore\n24. **\"Main Tera Boyfriend\"** - Raabta\n25. **\"Zaalima\"** - Raees\n\nThese songs cover a variety of moods and styles, making them versatile choices for different occasions. Whether you're looking for something romantic, upbeat, or soulful, there's a song in Hindi that fits the bill!",
